sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Browser as Frontend App
    participant Components as Frontend Components
    participant Backend as Backend API

    User->>Browser: Öffnet Anwendung
    activate Browser
    Browser->>Components: Lade und initialisiere Komponenten
    activate Components
    Components-->>Browser: Komponenten gerendert
    deactivate Components
    Browser->>Backend: API-Anfrage für Daten
    activate Backend
    Backend-->>Browser: Datenantwort
    deactivate Backend
    Browser->>Components: Übergabe von Daten / State-Update
    activate Components
    Components-->>Browser: UI aktualisiert
    deactivate Components
    Browser-->>User: UI anzeigen
    deactivate Browser